1 translation units
start translation unit 1
translation-unit
  function-definition f function of (bool, float) returning float
    parameter sign bool
    parameter x float
    compound-statement
      return-statement
        conditional-expression prvalue long double
          id-expression lvalue bool sign
          unary-expression prvalue float OP_MINUS:-
            id-expression lvalue float x
          literal prvalue long double 1.0L
end translation unit
